<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
<meta charset="utf-8">
<meta http-equiv="X-UA-Compatible" content="IE=edge">
<meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1">
<title>c20g Application Portal</title>

<!-- Stylesheets -->
<link href="common/lib/bootstrap/css/bootstrap.min.css" rel="stylesheet">
<link href="common/lib/datepicker/css/datepicker.css" rel="stylesheet">
<link href="common/lib/font-awesome/css/font-awesome.min.css" rel="stylesheet">
<link href="common/css/at-recruiting.css" rel="stylesheet">

</head>

<body>

	<div class="container">

		<div id="viewExternalApplicationForm">

  			<h1>Associate BPM Consultant Job Application</h1>
    
  			<div class="description"> 
    			<h3> Job Description and Qualifications </h3>
    			<p>Counterpoint Consulting, Inc. is a leading provider of process-focused enterprise software solutions. Our cloud and mobile-based business automation systems enable customers to optimize efficiency, agility, and organizational performance.</p>
    			<p>We have been providing enterprise architecture, software development, systems integration and administration, as well as post-production support and training to commercial and Federal customers on several leading commercial and open source Business Process Management (BPM) platforms since 2006.</p>
    			<p>As a Consultant at Counterpoint, you will:
      				<ul class='bullets'>
        				<li>Work with customers to identify and model business processes using commercial and oss BPM software</li>
        				<li>Work directly with our customers to translate business needs into technical solutions	</li>
        				<li>Design, develop and test software</li>
        				<li>Work independently or cooperatively within software development teams</li>
        				<li>Provide follow up support and training to our customers</li>
        				<li>Participate in internal software development projects </li>
      				</ul>
    			</p>
    			<p> Location: Vienna, VA</p>
    			<p> Travel: Must be willing to travel to customer sites (generally in the D.C. metro area) </p>
    			<p>Required Qualifications</p>
    			<p>We are looking for intelligent, responsible and committed individuals who possess:
      				<ul class="bullets">
        				<li>BA/BS from an accredited university</li>
        				<li>Demonstrated record of excellence inside and outside of the classroom</li>
        				<li>Software development experience or interest in pursuing a career in technology</li>
      				</ul>
    			</p>
    			<p>Preferred Qualifications
      				<ul class="bullets">
        				<li>BA/BS specifically in computer science or engineering</li>
        				<li>Knowledge of Web Development Technologies and Libraries (HTML, JS, CSS, jQuery)</li>
        				<li>Knowledge of Relational Databases &amp; SQL</li>
        				<li>Software development experience (Java, Java Web Frameworks and / or .NET)</li>
        				<li>BPM development experience with Appian, Cordys, Metastorm, Micropact, Pegasystems, Opentext, Fuijitsu or other commercial or open source BPMS</li>
      				</ul>
    			</p>
    			<p>Company Perks and Benefits
      				<ul class="bullets">
        				<li>Generous Paid Time Off</li>
        				<li>FREE medical insurance for employees</li>
        				<li>Flexible Spending Accounts (FSAs)</li>
        				<li>Short and Long Term Disability Insurance</li>
        				<li>401k with match</li>
        				<li>On site fitness center</li>
        				<li>Frequent company happy hours and social events</li>
        				<li>Casual dress code</li>
        				<li>A well-stocked kitchen with a large variety of beverages and snacks</li>
        				<li>A fun, open workspace, complete with a foosball table</li>
      				</ul>  
    			</p>  
  			</div> <!-- close description -->

			<form id="application_fields">
  
  				<legend><h3>Create Application</h3></legend>

    			<h3>Personal Information</h3>
    			
    			<fieldset class="personal_info nobullets" id="personal_info">
      			<ul>
        			<row>
          			<li class="col-md-6"> 
            			<label> First Name </label><span class="required"> *</span>
            			<input type="text" class="form-control" name="first_name" id="first_name"/>
          			</li>
          			<li class="col-md-6"> 
            			<label> Last Name </label><span class="required"> *</span>
            			<input type="text" class="form-control" name="last_name" id="last_name"/>
          			</li>
        			</row>
        <row>
          <li class="col-md-6">
            <label> Email </label><span class="required"> *</span>
            <input type="text" class="form-control" name="email" id="email" />
          </li>
          <li class="col-md-6">
            <label> Phone Number </label><span class="required"> *</span>
            <input type="text" class="form-control" name="phone_number" id="phone_number" />
          </li>
        </row>
        <row>
          <li class="col-md-12">
            <label> Home Address </label>
            <input type="text" class="form-control" name="street_address" id="street_address" placeholder="Street Address"/>
          </li>
        </row>
        <row>
          <li class="col-md-4">
            <input type="text" class="form-control" name="city" id="city" placeholder="City"/>
          </li>
          <li class="col-md-4">
            <input type="text" class="form-control" name="state" id="state" placeholder="State (Abbreviation)" maxlength="2"/>
          </li>
          <li class="col-md-4">
            <input type="text" class="form-control" name="zipcode" id="zipcode" placeholder="Zip Code" maxlength="10"/>
          </li>
        </row>
      </ul>   
    </fieldset>

  <br>

  <h3>Education</h3>

  <h4> College </h4>
    <fieldset class="education personal_info nobullets" id="education">
      <ul>
        <row>
          <li class="col-md-6"> 
            <select id="college_state" name="college_state">
              <option class="req_dropdown"> Select Institution State <span class="required"> *</span></option>
            </select>
          </li>  
          <li class="col-md-6"> 
            <select id="college_name" name="college_name">
              <option class="req_dropdown"> Select Institution Name <span class="required"> *</span></option>
            </select>
          </li>  
        </row> 
        <row>
          <li class="col-md-6">    
            <select id="primary_study" name="primary_study">
              <option> Primary Field of Study <span class="required"> *</span></option>
            </select>
          </li>
          <li class="col-md-6">
            <select id="secondary_study" name="secondary_study">
              <option> Secondary Field of Study </option>
            </select>
          </li>
        </row>
        <row>
          <li class="col-md-6">
            <label> GPA </label><span class="required"> *</span>
            <input type="text" name="gpa" id="gpa" class="form-control" placeholder="4.0 Scale"/>
          </li>
          <li class="col-md-6">
            <label> Graduation Date </label><span class="required"> *</span>
            <input type="text" name="grad_date" id="grad_date" class="form-control"/>
          </li>
        </row>
        <row>
          <li class="col-md-12">
            <label> Awards and Recognitions </label>
            <textarea id="awards" name="awards" placeholder="500 Character Limit" maxlength="500"></textarea>
          </li>
        </row>
      </ul>  
    </fieldset>

  <h4> Relevant Education </h4>
    <fieldset class="other_education personal_info nobullets" id="other_education">
      <ul>
        <row>
          <li class="col-md-12">
            <label> Have you completed any additional classes or programs? </label>
          </li>  
        </row>    
        <row>
          <li class="col-md-12"> 
            <select id="relevant_ed">
              <option> Select Program </option>
            </select>
          </li>  
        </row>
        <row>
          <li class="col-md-12"> 
            <div id="relevant_ed_info">
              <label> Please provide details: </label>
              <textarea id='relevant_ed_details' placeholder="500 Character Limit" maxlength="500"></textarea>
            </div> 
          </li>
        </row>
      </ul>  
    </fieldset>

<br>

  <h3> Additional Information</h3>
  <fieldset class="additional_information nobullets" id="additional_information">
    <ul>
      <row>
        <li class="col-md-12" id="marketing_source">
          <label> How did you hear about us? </label><span class="required"> *</span>
          <row>
            <form id='source'>
              <ul id="main_source_list" class="col-md-6">
                <li id="cf_li"><input type="checkbox" name="career_fair" id="career_fair">Career Fair</li>
              </ul> 
              <ul id="cf_source_list" class="col-md-6">
                <li><label>Select Career Fair:</label></li>
              </ul> 
            </form>  
          </row>
        </li>
      </row>
      <row>
        <li class="col-md-12">
          <div class="referral_employee">
            <label> Referring Counterpoint Employee </label>
            <input type='text' id='referrer'/>
          </div>
        </li>
      </row>
      <row>
        <li class="col-md-12">
          <label>What's your employment eligibility?</label><span class="required"> *</span>
          <select id="work_auth" required="required" aria-required="true" aria-invalid="false" class="valid">
            <option value>Select work status</option>
          </select>
        </li>
      </row>
      <row>
        <li class="col-md-6">
          <label> When are you available to start? </label><span class="required"> *</span>
          <input type='text' id='start_date' class="form-control"/>
        </li>
        <li class="col-md-6">
          <label> What is your desired salary? </label>
          <input type='text' id='desired_salary' class="form-control"/>
        </li>  
      </row>
      <row>
        <li class="col-md-12"> 
          <label> Is there anything else you'd like us to know about you?</label>
          <textarea id='other_info' placeholder="500 Character Limit" maxlength="500"></textarea>
        </li>
      </row>
      <row>
        <li><button class="btn btn-primary"><span class="glyphicon glyphicon-upload"></span> Resume <span class="required"> * </span></button></li>
      </row>
      <row>
        <li><button class="btn btn-primary"><span class="glyphicon glyphicon-upload"></span> Cover Letter </button></li>
      </row>
      <row>
        <li class="col-md-6">
          <input type='text' id='linked_in' class='form-control' placeholder='LinkedIn'/>
        </li>
        <li class="col-md-6">
          <input type='text' id='github' class='form-control' placeholder='GitHub'/>
        </li>
      </row>
      <row>
        <li class="col-md-6">
          <input type='text' id='personal_site' class='form-control' placeholder='Website/Portfolio'/>
        </li>
        <li class="col-md-6">
          <input type='text' id='twitter' class='form-control' placeholder='Twitter'/>
        </li>
      </row>
    </ul>  
  </fieldset>

  </form> <!-- closes application_fields div -->
</div> <!-- closes ViewExternalApplicationForm div -->


  <div class="wrapper">
   <button id="submitJobApplicationButton" type="submit" class="btn btn-primary">Submit</button>
   <button id="cancelJobApplicationButton" class="btn btn-warn" value="Cancel">Cancel</button>
  </div>
			</div>
		</div>

	</div>
	<!-- /container -->

	<!-- Javascript -->
  <script> 
    window.c20g = {}; 
  </script>
	<script src="common/lib/jquery/js/jquery-1.11.1.min.js"></script>
	<script src="common/lib/jquery/plugins/jquery-ui.min.js"></script>
	<script src="common/lib/jquery/plugins/jquery.soap.js"></script>
	<script src="common/lib/jquery/plugins/jquery.xml2json.js"></script>
